🎵 Spotify Analytics Dashboard — Power BI

A fully interactive Spotify-themed Power BI Dashboard analyzing music trends, artist popularity, and song metrics from the Global Top 50 charts. Built with AI-assisted DAX measures using Power BI's DAX Query View.

📊 Dashboard Overview
The dashboard is divided into 4 interactive pages:

🏠 Home — Landing page with navigation
📈 Overview — High-level KPIs and trend charts
🎤 Artists — Artist-level breakdown and rankings
🎵 Songs — Song-level analysis and metrics

